
& piloting-naval
 
 >> Help: Piloting-Naval (Piloting Skills)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Used for piloting rolls while in a naval unit.
 
 To see specifics on naval units, type 'help naval'.
 
 NOTE: This site does not currently support artillery, but we may have it in
       the near future.
 
 For a detailed look at this skill, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages

